   a. read from telegram
   b. translate to english
   c. transform to the summary of 77 chars using chatgpt solution
   d. store in the db, original text, the translation, the summary, the last published date, the rating from telegram, author etc
   e. when transforming, pay attention on billing, probably need make it in batches of 100
3. once it's done, write layer prog which will read from the db, oriented to the last published date and provide texts to CLIP
4. clip should select most matchable item and then based on the data, need publish to telegram!!
